headline: Here's How Much Traders Expect Accenture Stock To Move After Friday's Earnings
summary: Accenture is set to post earnings for the third quarter of fiscal 2025 on Friday morning, with markets anticipating the professional services firm's stock could reach a two-month low or a three-month high following its report.
